summary: This is an email chain from July 2019 discussing a list of victims of Jeffrey Epstein represented by attorneys. The sender notes that the list may not be comprehensive and mentions that some victims are not on the official list, indicating ongoing efforts to identify and represent victims.
keyFacts: The email discusses a list of Epstein victims represented by attorneys, noting it may not be comprehensive.
The sender indicates there are victims not on the official list and seeks permission to add names provided by another attorney.
The correspondence is marked as confidential and subject to attorney-client privilege, indicating legal representation of victims.
